Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.83,0:00:35.25,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}叶いたい事が　溢れてるから
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.58,0:00:40.94,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}立ち止まってる　暇なんてないよね
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.35,0:00:44.44,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}胸に秘めたあこがれを
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.44,0:00:47.38,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}フルボリュームで届けよう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.40,0:00:52.28,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}行こう…クレッシェンドの向こうへ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.33,0:00:58.39,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}つまずいてもいい　はみだしてもいい
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.47,0:01:06.90,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}君の音色を　僕たちは待っている
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.88,0:01:15.49,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}響け!　生まれたての夢つめ込んで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.70,0:01:21.46,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}大きな空へ　いま旅立とう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.48,0:01:27.13,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}拓け!　笑顔を味方につけて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.21,0:01:32.95,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}離さない　諦めたくない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.96,0:01:38.15,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}限界さえも　跳ね返す勇気で
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.58,0:01:42.41,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}DREAM SOLISTER
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.83,0:00:35.25,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}因為有太多心願
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.58,0:00:40.94,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}所以無暇停滯不前
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.35,0:00:44.44,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}將心底秘藏的憧憬
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.44,0:00:47.38,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}乘上最大的音量
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.40,0:00:52.28,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}傳達到漸強記號的彼方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.33,0:00:58.39,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}遭遇挫折也好 合不上拍也罷
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.47,0:01:06.90,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}我們都期待著你的美妙音色
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.88,0:01:15.49,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}奏響樂器 滿懷初生的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.70,0:01:21.46,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}向著廣闊天空 現在踏上旅途
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.48,0:01:27.13,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}敞開胸懷 讓笑容成為夥伴
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.21,0:01:32.95,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}不會放手 不願放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.96,0:01:38.15,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}鼓起勇氣 衝破界限
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.58,0:01:42.41,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}成為夢想的獨奏者
Comment: 0,0:01:42.41,0:01:44.41,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.41,0:02:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真是純淨的音色
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.50,0:02:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好像能傳到無窮無際一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.78,0:02:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.96,0:02:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.02,0:02:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以再讓我多聽一聽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.46,0:02:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}聽一聽學姐的小號
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.94,0:02:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我真的很想聽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.77,0:02:24.64,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(350,0)\blur2\bord1.8\3c&HAA6D5B&\c&HFEFEFE&\pos(710,520)}歡迎回來 試音
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.37,0:02:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.57,0:02:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}長號第23小節
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.05,0:02:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}第二聲部的同學能單獨演奏一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.36,0:02:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.50,0:02:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不 還是一個一個來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.89,0:02:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}塚本同學
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.81,0:02:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.42,0:03:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}塚本同學 我上週就一再強調
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.22,0:03:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}請你練好那一段吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.27,0:03:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.57,0:03:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒有時間因為這一段一直重來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.63,0:03:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}請在明天前練好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.45,0:03:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.44,0:03:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那麼再下一段 一起來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.62,0:03:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.34,0:03:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}三…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.01,0:03:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好熱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.25,0:03:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們去外面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.81,0:03:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不愧是夏天
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.59,0:03:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}久美子會怕熱嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.23,0:03:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要選的話 我覺得天氣冷還比較好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.63,0:03:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我喜歡夏天
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.46,0:03:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是小號聲部的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.71,0:03:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.26,0:03:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}高坂同學也會來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.21,0:03:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要一起去吃飯嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.81,0:03:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}咦…但首先是我們聲部不同
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.13,0:03:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}「首先」的問題而已 對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.11,0:03:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯 「首先」而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.81,0:03:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}謝謝 我去叫她
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.84,0:03:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}說「想跟你一起吃」不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.20,0:03:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真有她的風格 但小綠我很喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.46,0:04:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在老地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.78,0:04:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}先失陪了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.83,0:04:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你覺得如何
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.90,0:04:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.53,0:04:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你覺得這吹得怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.03,0:04:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我覺得很棒 非常好聽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.92,0:04:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}音色很美 音量也很大
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.49,0:04:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}很…很適合獨奏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.82,0:04:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}對不…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.59,0:04:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.38,0:04:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一年級生就能吹出這樣的聲音 太不講理了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.08,0:04:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}根本是犯規
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.37,0:04:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.02,0:05:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我想問你吃過午餐了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.61,0:05:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.74,0:05:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這樣啊 原本還想找你一起去吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.09,0:05:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不要緊 我剛剛和香織學姐她們一起吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.45,0:05:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.93,0:05:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.42,0:05:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯 香織學姐非常關心我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.86,0:05:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們還是能作為北高管樂社一員
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.13,0:05:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一起在大賽上演奏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.02,0:05:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}來一場精彩的演奏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.81,0:05:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.63,0:05:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}香織學姐真是個好人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.48,0:05:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯 所以才有點糾結
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.36,0:05:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.94,0:05:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.36,0:06:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.23,0:06:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不是挺好的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.65,0:06:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}又是這個回答？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.13,0:06:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}上次問你 你也這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.83,0:06:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因為吹得一樣 所以回答也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.05,0:06:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是挺好的 但也僅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.57,0:06:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}而且做決定的也不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.41,0:06:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}碳酸飲料…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.21,0:06:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哦 原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.94,0:06:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那要先提前幫你熱烈慶祝一下？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.73,0:06:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那我換個問法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.53,0:06:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.73,0:06:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}明日香覺得誰比較適合？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.02,0:06:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我覺得誰吹得好誰就適合
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.45,0:06:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}瀧老師似乎就是以此為基準決定的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.84,0:06:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}也就是說高坂同學比較好？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.13,0:06:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}都說了 問我這個有什麼意義呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.90,0:06:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}做決定的又不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.21,0:06:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.28,0:06:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我想知道…你心裡是怎麼想的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.76,0:06:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}說出來真的好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.49,0:06:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不 我不希望你說出口
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.96,0:06:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就算是玩笑 我也不想聽你說高坂同學比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.40,0:07:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我沒說過那種話吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.96,0:07:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還是說你有超能力 能讀出我的思考？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.72,0:07:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.12,0:07:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那麼明天就在禮堂練習
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.85,0:07:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}請當成正式演出 認真練習吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.55,0:07:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.23,0:07:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}聲部長和搬運樂器的同學留下來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.44,0:07:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要說明天的安排
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.33,0:07:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.10,0:07:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.07,0:07:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.96,0:07:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以請別再無視一年級生了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.16,0:07:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.37,0:07:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們又沒有無視
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.22,0:07:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是那些一年級的自說自話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.16,0:07:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.05,0:07:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你在發什麼呆？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.70,0:08:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}煩死了 別管我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.89,0:08:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒在想些多餘的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.06,0:08:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}什麼意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.94,0:08:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我先說清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.01,0:08:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}會傷心的可是香織學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.53,0:08:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.43,0:08:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}明明連試音都沒過 還在那跩什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.74,0:08:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.72,0:08:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我知道！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.35,0:08:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那種事我當然知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.09,0:08:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}都傍晚了還這麼熱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.77,0:08:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}明天是在禮堂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.72,0:08:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你們那邊是怎麼練習的？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.80,0:08:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}老師要我們沒過試音的人演奏好一首曲子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.01,0:08:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大家都在練習呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.74,0:08:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你想 低音號只有我一個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.22,0:08:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}低音也就我和夏紀學姐兩個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.41,0:08:41.69,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}下一站 黃檗 黃檗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.82,0:08:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好像挺有趣的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.07,0:08:44.50,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}電車和月台之間有空隙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.08,0:08:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯 挺有趣的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.11,0:08:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我得好好支持大家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.00,0:08:48.21,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要下車的乘客請注意腳下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.96,0:08:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.86,0:08:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯 明天見
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.27,0:08:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}石蛾好討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.34,0:09:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.05,0:09:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}想吹好啊 好一點…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.53,0:09:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}抱歉 突然叫住你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.13,0:09:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不會 想說的是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.69,0:09:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}麗奈…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.41,0:09:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是關於試音的事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.81,0:09:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.42,0:09:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}8點要集合的 注意時間
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.05,0:09:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.09,0:09:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.17,0:09:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.03,0:09:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}無論如何…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.17,0:09:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}無論如何我都想讓香織學姐吹獨奏聲部
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.52,0:09:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以…求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.93,0:09:59.97,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\bord0\3c&HFFFFFF&\c&H000000&\pos(240,242)}低音號
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.93,0:09:59.97,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\c&HBDA40F&\3c&HFFFFFF&\pos(232,238)}低音號
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.98,0:10:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你是要我故意輸掉嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.76,0:10:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要是被揭穿了 說是我威脅你的也可以
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.03,0:10:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}說我欺負你了也沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.89,0:10:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.12,0:10:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就算不這麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.18,0:10:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}只要香織學姐試音時吹得比我好就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.69,0:10:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我知道的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.60,0:10:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}去年 社團裡吹得最好的就是香織學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.70,0:10:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但還是依照年級排序
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.20,0:10:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}獨奏是由完全沒有練習過的高年級生來吹的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.30,0:10:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不止如此
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.42,0:10:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}香織學姐為了留住想退出的一年級生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.38,0:10:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還打算回絕參加大賽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.91,0:10:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但他們還是都退出了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.58,0:10:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以大賽上的演奏也是一團糟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.64,0:10:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這沒關係吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.99,0:10:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這種事跟我沒關係吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.85,0:10:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}對 沒關係 完全沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.48,0:11:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是你還有明年 還有後年
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.75,0:11:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有瀧老師在 管樂社也會變得越來越好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.41,0:11:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但香織學姐是最後一次了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.67,0:11:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}今年就是她最後的機會了 所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.67,0:11:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}請不要這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.78,0:11:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}失陪了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.14,0:11:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.43,0:11:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}比賽會場的禮堂比這裡還要大
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.43,0:11:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這樣就吃驚 到時可是會被嚇倒的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.15,0:11:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}也 也對
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.52,0:11:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不過我們都不用參賽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.76,0:11:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但以後還有機會嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.46,0:11:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}樂器來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.28,0:11:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒事的人來幫忙一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.97,0:11:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好了 各位 開始做準備吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.93,0:11:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.66,0:11:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}中世古同學 高坂同學
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.34,0:11:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.24,0:12:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你們就不用整理場地了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.70,0:12:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為試音做準備吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.18,0:12:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.87,0:12:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不用擺這麼擠吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.66,0:12:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這又不是音樂教室
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.70,0:12:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}對哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.01,0:12:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你看 那邊還空著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.79,0:12:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.63,0:12:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}明日香 別管這了 去看看香織吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.63,0:12:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.51,0:12:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}她肯定想和你聊兩句
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.70,0:12:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不過我是副社長啊 怎麼能擅自離開
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.58,0:12:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你老是在這種時候才這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.70,0:12:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}啊 先從木管樂器開始擺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.01,0:12:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好 抱歉借過一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.10,0:12:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}對了 這邊能交給你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.57,0:12:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯 沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.81,0:12:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}狀態怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.40,0:12:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯 沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.81,0:12:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還要準備場地 你也過去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.89,0:13:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.23,0:13:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}學姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.65,0:13:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.77,0:13:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.29,0:13:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}請加油
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.49,0:13:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.21,0:13:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}香織
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.33,0:13:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}緊張嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.04,0:13:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不用特地來看我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.94,0:13:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你可是社長哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.97,0:13:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}也就是掛個名而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.54,0:13:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}搞得我像婚禮前的新娘子一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.59,0:13:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以有什麼事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.41,0:13:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不是身為社長
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.69,0:13:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我想作為和你一起走過三年的夥伴 說幾句話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.47,0:14:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}希望你能接受
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.15,0:14:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.19,0:14:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還有 明日香不會來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.89,0:14:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.34,0:14:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}對了 我之前就想問了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.80,0:14:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為什麼是明日香？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.09,0:14:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為什麼你那麼在意她
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.91,0:14:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為什麼呢 我也不太清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.44,0:14:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}感覺好像被她看透了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.27,0:14:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我所想的全被看穿了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.31,0:14:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以我想讓明日香吃一驚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.58,0:14:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我希望真正的我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.27,0:14:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}能夠比明日香想像的我 走得更遠一步
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.63,0:14:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大概是這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.49,0:14:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還真麻煩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.16,0:14:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就是說啊 真麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.09,0:14:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}差不多準備好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.79,0:14:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.14,0:14:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.92,0:14:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.50,0:15:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}久美子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.60,0:15:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}如果…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.22,0:15:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}如果我輸了 你會不開心嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.75,0:15:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}麗奈…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.17,0:15:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我會…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.72,0:15:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我當然會！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.26,0:15:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.36,0:15:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}麗奈不是要成為獨一無二的人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.57,0:15:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.64,0:15:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}麗奈和別人不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.92,0:15:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}麗奈和任何人都不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.73,0:15:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你不能被旁人左右
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.39,0:15:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這種事不是愚蠢透頂的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.37,0:15:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.14,0:15:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}如果我現在贏了 就會成為壞人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.49,0:15:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}壞人就壞人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.60,0:15:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}到時候我也陪你一起當壞人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.64,0:15:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你就是比香織學姐強
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.82,0:15:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}獨奏就是該讓麗奈來吹
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.46,0:15:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我就這樣告訴他們
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.86,0:15:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.05,0:16:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大概…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.18,0:16:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}久美子的個性果然很差
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.82,0:16:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}會陪在我身邊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.61,0:16:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.96,0:16:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不會背叛我？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.49,0:16:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}如果背叛 你就殺了我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.49,0:16:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我真的會殺了你的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.47,0:16:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}麗奈的話可能真的會下手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.71,0:16:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我就是知道這個才說的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.21,0:16:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因為…這是愛的告白
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.41,0:16:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}麗奈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.19,0:16:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒問題 我一開始就完全沒有要輸的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.71,0:17:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那麼 接下來進行小號獨奏聲部的試音
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.29,0:17:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}等兩位吹完後
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.12,0:17:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}以各位的掌聲來決定人選吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.10,0:17:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這樣可以嗎 中世古同學
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.32,0:17:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.25,0:17:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}高坂同學
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.43,0:17:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.86,0:17:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那麼中世古同學 由你先開始
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.93,0:17:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.96,0:18:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}謝謝各位
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.89,0:18:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那麼接下來是高坂同學 請開始
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.87,0:18:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是
